{% # Group block v1.5.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v1.5.0 — color scheme becomes an explicit local override: new `custom_color_scheme` checkbox (default false) gates the `color_scheme` picker (`visible_if`); the snippet emits `color-scheme:<id>` only when checked (was: emit whenever the optional picker was set). `color_scheme` gains the now-required `default: scheme-1`, hidden until the checkbox is on. See `.context/docs/schema-conventions.md` § Color-scheme override.
  - v1.4.0 — replace `bleed` checkbox with `bleed_desktop` (none/inline_start/inline_end/both) + `bleed_mobile` (none/both) responsive enum API. Bleed positioning moves from the snippet's own CSS to the section's named-line bleed grid (per subgrid migration). Merchants previously setting `bleed: true` reset to `bleed_desktop: none`; opt back into bleed via the new enums.
  - v1.3.0 — add `container_style` setting (metaobject ref). Emits `container-style:<handle>` modifier; centralized CSS for card/outlined/elevated variants lives in `core.css` `@layer theme`.
  - v1.2.0 — replace `@theme` blocks wildcard with an explicit whitelist of the 9 shipped L1 blocks per the block-whitelisting convention in `composition-strategy.md`
  - v1.1.0 — add `bleed` checkbox to extend the group past the section gutter to the visible viewport width
  - v1.0.1 — `horizontal_alignment.info` clarifies that "Space between" only applies in row direction
  - v1.0.0 — initial
{% endcomment %}

{% capture contents %}{% content_for 'blocks' %}{% endcapture %}

